r Hereafter and Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20775,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/25\/sufyan-know-your-self\/","url_meta":{"origin":36646,"position":1},"title":"Sufyan on Confidence: If you know your self, you will not be harmed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Mubarak reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you know yourself, you will not be harmed by whatever is said about you.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 6\/390 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0641\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0636\u064f\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e 6\/390 \u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/28\/sufyan-zuhd-hikmah-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36646,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Zuhd: He gains wisdom once he forsakes worldly life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhen a servant renounces the world, Allah will cause wisdom to grow in his heart and to come forth from his tongue. He will grant him insight into the faults of the world, its diseases, and its cures.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":64,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/10\/10\/hiyat-al-dunya-parable\/","url_meta":{"origin":36646,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Worldly life is nothing compared to Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mustawrid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat is the parable of this worldly life, in comparison to the Hereafter, but one of you dipping his finger in the sea? Let him see what he brings forth.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2858 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/08\/sultan-allah-honors\/","url_meta":{"origin":36646,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Allah honors those who respect His authority","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 8, 2023","